---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="¿Quiénes somos?" id="intro">
  <Icon slot="eyebrow" name="logo-club-blanco" class="h-32" />
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    Somos un grupo de personas de Villaverde (y alrededores) que compartimos una misma pasión:
    <span class="text-primary">correr</span>.
    El club está gestionado por un grupo de socios y está vinculado a la Asociación Vecinal
    <span class="text-primary"> La Incolora</span></span>.
  </Fragment>
  <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ov6RcXRi0FA?si=1WoC5mKlBXHSDXnd" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="mailto:clubatletismovillaverde.com"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
      target="_blank"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="email" class="h-8" />
      <span>Contáctanos!</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1et7CS5jVLRLQVlgG9luEC5Vfk3Ha3n_9Vf4QG7gtkos"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
      target="_blank"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="rocket" class="h-8" />
      <span>Únete!</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
